txt.en: Collect a bucket from the Foul Larder
A bucket can be found in the Foul Larder in the dungeons of Barad-dûr.
Fill the bucket with water from the washing-tub
A washing-tub can be found in the Foul Larder in the dungeons of Barad-dûr.
Exhausted Stout-axes can be found throughout the dungeons of Barad-dûr.
You fill the bucket with water from the washing-tub
You are fated to labour in service to the Dark Lord.

Many Stout-axes cannot endure the harsh treatment of the Dark Lord.
